{"tid":186900,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人知我隻貓做咩事(求救po)[有圖]","createTime":"2017-04-04T14:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T20:23:44.000Z","uid":32780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e548fe5bb4d3f81e328ee888a507cfc3bc7fb80","tid":186900,"uid":32780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"上星期見到屋企隻貓下巴出黑點點，紅左甩毛，之後去睇獸醫話生癬，幫佢日日洗下巴搽癬藥，點知無變好反而仲衰過之前。想知係咪真係癬黎，我上網research揾有啲人話毛囊炎。有無人可以介紹一啲比較好嘅獸醫？近返屯門荃灣嘅有無巴絲介紹？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y0Jv3A0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy0Jv3A0.jpg&h=15ddafd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"650ed3bb22ddfcd34c8a3d3ce4b8400c621dc342","tid":186900,"uid":10115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:10:42.000Z","msg":"我睇開元朗專一 主人感冒同絕育都係呢間<br />\n兩次都好快好返"},{"pid":"8d65ecdab1939c7c49bcd03644dd0e480721c672","tid":186900,"uid":10115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:11:35.000Z","msg":"聽過朋友隻貓生癬但唔係咁嘅樣"},{"pid":"12b9a7814c0ef6db97a01e53f0dea6a3ee244050","tid":186900,"uid":32780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇開元朗專一 主人感冒同絕育都係呢間<br />\n兩次都好快好返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我尋日book左仁愛，呢間ching有無睇過？唔知好唔好，如果唔好我立即轉專一"},{"pid":"666b500ce52eec5cbaadd9cc18d8b4cbfbbba0cf","tid":186900,"uid":32780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽過朋友隻貓生癬但唔係咁嘅樣</blockquote><br />\n就係之前佢生過癬好似唔係咁，同埋勤力搽藥洗好快好返，而家無好仲多左撻，好心急。"},{"pid":"fbb866b4463cafa8e130124520eb9fb579bedce0","tid":186900,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"係咪貓黑頭再發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae96d8edefaa236fbd97f2165b53ca2b1ee4d162","tid":186900,"uid":32780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪貓黑頭再發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/